### Development Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/epappas/anvil-testcontainer.git
cd anvil-testcontainer

poetry install

poetry run pytest
```

### Testing

Run the test suite:

```bash
poetry run pytest
```

With coverage:

```bash
poetry run pytest --cov=anvil_testcontainer
```

